trans-unit.source: Provides an abstract class for controls that allow multiple items to be selected.
trans-unit.target: Fornece uma classe abstrata para controles que permitem que vários itens sejam selecionados.

trans-unit.source: When you derive a class from the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Primitives.MultiSelector> class, set the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Primitives.MultiSelector.CanSelectMultipleItems%2A> property to `true` to allow multi-selection in your control.
trans-unit.target: Quando você derivar uma classe a partir de <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Primitives.MultiSelector> classe, defina o <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Primitives.MultiSelector.CanSelectMultipleItems%2A> propriedade para `true` para permitir várias seleções em seu controle.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Windows.Controls.Primitives.MultiSelector" /> class.
trans-unit.target: Inicializa uma nova instância da classe <see cref="T:System.Windows.Controls.Primitives.MultiSelector" />.

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Primitives.MultiSelector> is an abstract class and cannot be instantiated directly.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Primitives.MultiSelector> é uma classe abstrata e não pode ser instanciado diretamente.

trans-unit.source: Starts a new selection transaction.
trans-unit.target: Inicia uma nova transação de seleção.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Primitives.MultiSelector.BeginUpdateSelectedItems%2A> method sets <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Primitives.MultiSelector.IsUpdatingSelectedItems%2A> to `true`.
trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Primitives.MultiSelector.BeginUpdateSelectedItems%2A> método conjuntos <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Primitives.MultiSelector.IsUpdatingSelectedItems%2A> para `true`.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Primitives.MultiSelector.EndUpdateSelectedItems%2A> method sets <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Primitives.MultiSelector.IsUpdatingSelectedItems%2A> to `false`.
trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Primitives.MultiSelector.EndUpdateSelectedItems%2A> método conjuntos <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Primitives.MultiSelector.IsUpdatingSelectedItems%2A> para `false`.

trans-unit.source: The following example shows how to use the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Primitives.MultiSelector.BeginUpdateSelectedItems%2A> method in a class derived from <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Primitives.MultiSelector>.
trans-unit.target: O exemplo a seguir mostra como usar o <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Primitives.MultiSelector.BeginUpdateSelectedItems%2A> método em uma classe derivada de <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Primitives.MultiSelector>.

trans-unit.source: <see cref="P:System.Windows.Controls.Primitives.MultiSelector.IsUpdatingSelectedItems" /> is <see langword="true" /> when this method is called.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="P:System.Windows.Controls.Primitives.MultiSelector.IsUpdatingSelectedItems" /> é <see langword="true" /> quando este método é chamado.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets a value that indicates whether the multiple items in the <see cref="T:System.Windows.Controls.Primitives.MultiSelector" /> can be selected at a time.
trans-unit.target: Obtém ou define um valor que indica se vários itens do <see cref="T:System.Windows.Controls.Primitives.MultiSelector" /> podem ser selecionados ao mesmo tempo.

trans-unit.source: <see langword="true" /> if multiple items in the <see cref="T:System.Windows.Controls.Primitives.MultiSelector" /> can be selected at a time; otherwise, <see langword="false" />.
trans-unit.target: <see langword="true" /> se vários itens no <see cref="T:System.Windows.Controls.Primitives.MultiSelector" /> puderem ser selecionados ao mesmo tempo; caso contrário, <see langword="false" />.

trans-unit.source: Set the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Primitives.MultiSelector.CanSelectMultipleItems%2A> property to `true` in a derived class to allow multi-selection for that class.
trans-unit.target: Definir o <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Primitives.MultiSelector.CanSelectMultipleItems%2A> propriedade `true` em uma classe derivada para permitir várias seleções para essa classe.

trans-unit.source: The following code example shows how to set this property in a derived class.
trans-unit.target: O exemplo de código a seguir mostra como definir essa propriedade em uma classe derivada.

trans-unit.source: Commits the selected items to the <see cref="T:System.Windows.Controls.Primitives.MultiSelector" />.
trans-unit.target: Confirma os itens selecionados para o <see cref="T:System.Windows.Controls.Primitives.MultiSelector" />.

trans-unit.source: This method sets <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Primitives.MultiSelector.IsUpdatingSelectedItems%2A> to `false` and updates the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Primitives.MultiSelector.SelectedItems%2A> collection.
trans-unit.target: Esse método define <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Primitives.MultiSelector.IsUpdatingSelectedItems%2A> para `false` e atualiza o <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Primitives.MultiSelector.SelectedItems%2A> coleção.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Primitives.MultiSelector.BeginUpdateSelectedItems%2A> method sets <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Primitives.MultiSelector.IsUpdatingSelectedItems%2A> to `true`.
trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Primitives.MultiSelector.BeginUpdateSelectedItems%2A> método conjuntos <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Primitives.MultiSelector.IsUpdatingSelectedItems%2A> para `true`.

trans-unit.source: The following example shows how to use the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Primitives.MultiSelector.EndUpdateSelectedItems%2A> method in a class derived from <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Primitives.MultiSelector>.
trans-unit.target: O exemplo a seguir mostra como usar o <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Primitives.MultiSelector.EndUpdateSelectedItems%2A> método em uma classe derivada de <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Primitives.MultiSelector>.

trans-unit.source: <see cref="P:System.Windows.Controls.Primitives.MultiSelector.IsUpdatingSelectedItems" /> is <see langword="false" /> when this method is called.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="P:System.Windows.Controls.Primitives.MultiSelector.IsUpdatingSelectedItems" /> é <see langword="false" /> quando este método é chamado.

trans-unit.source: Gets a value that indicates whether the <see cref="T:System.Windows.Controls.Primitives.MultiSelector" /> is currently performing a bulk update to the <see cref="P:System.Windows.Controls.Primitives.MultiSelector.SelectedItems" /> collection.
trans-unit.target: Obtém um valor que indica se o <see cref="T:System.Windows.Controls.Primitives.MultiSelector" /> está executando uma atualização em massa para a coleção <see cref="P:System.Windows.Controls.Primitives.MultiSelector.SelectedItems" /> no momento.

trans-unit.source: <see langword="true" /> if the <see cref="T:System.Windows.Controls.Primitives.MultiSelector" /> is currently performing a bulk update to the <see cref="P:System.Windows.Controls.Primitives.MultiSelector.SelectedItems" /> collection; otherwise, <see langword="false" />.
trans-unit.target: <see langword="true" /> se o <see cref="T:System.Windows.Controls.Primitives.MultiSelector" /> está executando uma atualização em massa para a coleção <see cref="P:System.Windows.Controls.Primitives.MultiSelector.SelectedItems" /> no momento; caso contrário, <see langword="false" />.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Primitives.MultiSelector.BeginUpdateSelectedItems%2A> method sets <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Primitives.MultiSelector.IsUpdatingSelectedItems%2A> to `true`.
trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Primitives.MultiSelector.BeginUpdateSelectedItems%2A> método conjuntos <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Primitives.MultiSelector.IsUpdatingSelectedItems%2A> para `true`.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Primitives.MultiSelector.EndUpdateSelectedItems%2A> method sets <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Primitives.MultiSelector.IsUpdatingSelectedItems%2A> to `false`.
trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Primitives.MultiSelector.EndUpdateSelectedItems%2A> método conjuntos <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Primitives.MultiSelector.IsUpdatingSelectedItems%2A> para `false`.

trans-unit.source: The following example shows how to use the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Primitives.MultiSelector.IsUpdatingSelectedItems%2A> property in a class derived from <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Primitives.MultiSelector>.
trans-unit.target: O exemplo a seguir mostra como usar o <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Primitives.MultiSelector.IsUpdatingSelectedItems%2A> propriedade em uma classe derivada de <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Primitives.MultiSelector>.

trans-unit.source: Selects all of the items in the <see cref="T:System.Windows.Controls.Primitives.MultiSelector" />.
trans-unit.target: Seleciona todos os itens no <see cref="T:System.Windows.Controls.Primitives.MultiSelector" />.

trans-unit.source: You can use this method only if <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Primitives.MultiSelector.CanSelectMultipleItems%2A> is `true`.
trans-unit.target: Você pode use esse método somente se <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Primitives.MultiSelector.CanSelectMultipleItems%2A> é `true`.

trans-unit.source: <see cref="P:System.Windows.Controls.Primitives.MultiSelector.CanSelectMultipleItems" /> is <see langword="false" />.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="P:System.Windows.Controls.Primitives.MultiSelector.CanSelectMultipleItems" /> é <see langword="false" />.

trans-unit.source: Gets the items in the <see cref="T:System.Windows.Controls.Primitives.MultiSelector" /> that are selected.
trans-unit.target: Obtém os itens no <see cref="T:System.Windows.Controls.Primitives.MultiSelector" /> selecionados.

trans-unit.source: The items in the <see cref="T:System.Windows.Controls.Primitives.MultiSelector" /> that are selected.
trans-unit.target: Os itens no <see cref="T:System.Windows.Controls.Primitives.MultiSelector" /> selecionados.

trans-unit.source: If <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Primitives.MultiSelector.CanSelectMultipleItems%2A> is `false`, you cannot add more than one item to the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Primitives.MultiSelector.SelectedItems%2A> collection.
trans-unit.target: Se <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Primitives.MultiSelector.CanSelectMultipleItems%2A> é `false`, você não pode adicionar mais de um item para o <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Primitives.MultiSelector.SelectedItems%2A> coleção.

trans-unit.source: Attempts to do so will cause an exception.
trans-unit.target: Tentar fazer isso fará com que uma exceção.

trans-unit.source: Unselects all of the items in the <see cref="T:System.Windows.Controls.Primitives.MultiSelector" />.
trans-unit.target: Desmarca todos os itens no <see cref="T:System.Windows.Controls.Primitives.MultiSelector" />.

trans-unit.source: You can use this method regardless of whether <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Primitives.MultiSelector.CanSelectMultipleItems%2A> is `true` or `false`.
trans-unit.target: Você pode usar esse método independentemente se <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Primitives.MultiSelector.CanSelectMultipleItems%2A> é `true` ou `false`.
